{"tid":1556573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[教材] 齊上齊落唔係得把口講 請施出你慷慨之手幫手足","createTime":"2019-09-09T19:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T20:22:09.000Z","uid":217242,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1072e6023c111122e5eea80e5eb824dc55e747b7","tid":1556573,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:25:09.000Z","msg":"唔想講咁多 <br />\n已經好無奈 講到口臭<br />\n希望下次各位俾d勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落得現場就要有準備<br />\n呢幾個月真係發過唔少次呢d惡夢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">齊上齊落唔係得把口講</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">革命</span></span>亦唔係玩玩下叫口號<br />\n下次麻煩如有機會請救手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢可以為你犧牲<br />\n唔該你都攞d勇氣出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n負面教材 亦係 現實情況<br />\n希望大家以後唔好再<span style=\"color: brown;\">重蹈覆轍 以此為鑒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100335937981067/posts/127552021926125?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100335937981067%2Fposts%2F127552021926125%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=794c9aa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100335937981067/posts/127552021926125?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"c3418c4d26312accf99681ae48885002f7b4a09d","tid":1556573,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:26:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">救人唔該 多謝幫推</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好人一生平安</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d38a08d6db95a56aae0c5a007e3b4c173d1196b","tid":1556573,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r